                                ğŸ‡¸ğŸ‡¦ Test Arabic
                            </button>
                            <button onclick="testBannerFunction('en')" class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                                ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸ Test English
